          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Col max</td><td class="pr-4 text-green-300">(col-max m c)</td><td class="font-sans">Best the row player can get in that column</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4">Solution theorem</td><td class="pr-4 text-green-300">(all-eq-values-same? m)</td><td class="font-sans">All equilibria in a zero-sum game share one value</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
